HEADWORD: Imbow
<hw>Im*bow"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>im-</ets> in + <ets>bow</ets>. Cf. <er>Embow</er>.]</ety> <def>To
make like a bow; to curve; to arch; to vault; to embow.</def>
